{"tid":257993,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"膝頭對下少少好痛 除左睇醫生仲可以點？","createTime":"2017-05-25T16:31:51.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-26T11:11:03.000Z","uid":82919,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"1e8234b380157546f5a4dd21fd58cd895ddf3bab","tid":257993,"uid":82919,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-25T16:31:51.000Z","msg":"小弟就打開波嘅 平時好跳得 但都無話特別痛 不過每逢打風落雨 左邊膝頭都會小小痛<br />\n呢個禮拜唔知點解無啦啦開始 今日又落街打波 跟住痛到仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n除左睇醫生有無解決方法 例如 飲食 早訓 個啲？"},{"pid":"dabf8255fc6674e4582cf5a82036c3b4c8d7fa1f","tid":257993,"uid":47480,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-25T16:35:14.000Z","msg":"風濕"},{"pid":"c43463d1054b4ef1a36ea48614ea6f9faaf80a1b","tid":257993,"uid":82919,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-25T16:36:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>風濕</blockquote><br />\n今年先就黎20歲 咁快有<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5356ab83fa2eee29f2499c3a7b50ff13cb4a5802","tid":257993,"uid":118945,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-25T16:41:43.000Z","msg":"呢d位可能關關節或者韌帶事都唔定<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n而家唔醫好手尾長啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5cbcac4fdd5cb45b15f1291f68ba1b2dbdbd320b","tid":257993,"uid":82919,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-25T16:47:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>呢d位可能關關節或者韌帶事都唔定<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n而家唔醫好手尾長啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n多謝你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmo