N&quot; 痛既可能係勞損. 抖一排無事<br />\n但刺痛就有機會關 條_帶事"},{"pid":"fc51fb4311f49af1e7d0cdfea8df8d35ff72fa55","tid":257993,"uid":22772,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-26T07:32:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>一個點痛<br />\n定係成個關節都痛？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n一個點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n岩岩菠蘿蓋對下個個位？<br />\n係咪loading越大越痛，e.g. 跳高落地個陣</blockquote><br />\n我係,想知係咩事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n應該係patellar tendinopathy, <br />\n又或者叫jumpers knee<br />\n即係條patellar tendon 發炎<br />\n依家唔做運動個陣有冇痛？</blockquote><br />\n唔會 大力少少摸就痛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"http://bjsm.bmj.com/content/bjsports/39/2/102/F2.large.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbjsm.bmj.com%2Fcontent%2Fbjsports%2F39%2F2%2F102%2FF2.large.jpg&h=fe9710e1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n再問多少少, <br />\n如果你做A呢個動作, 可以引發到同樣位置既痛<br />\n咁就應該係patellar tendinopathy</blockquote><br />\n我做A會痛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 謝解答<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咁你9成9係patellar tendinopathy<br />\n依家應該要做既係休息+練返條tendon既strength<br />\ne.g. 靠牆坐/squat, 但唔使上落, 淨係hold個動作<br />\n同埋每次做運動都一定要做warm-up, cool down<br />\n帶返走d metabolic waste, 對healing有幫助<br />\n<br />\n如果真係要繼續打波, 可以戴條jumper's knee strap<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.halfpriceperfumes.co.uk/img/p/1/4/4/6/5/0/144650-large.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.halfpriceperfumes.co.uk%2Fimg%2Fp%2F1%2F4%2F4%2F6%2F5%2F0%2F144650-large.jpg&h=a069f43f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n將條strap硬既地方壓係你痛既位正上方<br />\n咁就可以spread開d stress</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 真係好感謝你<br />\n呢個痛都困擾左我兩三年<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n兩三年你都唔搵醫生睇下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nBTW, 坐牆個動作可以做30s- 1min/set, 3 set, rest 1 min<br />\n覺得有進步可以做squat (都係hold), 再來就做單腳squat hold<br />\n如果一轉動作, 24hr後仍然覺得會痛, 咁就做返上一個<br />\n如單腳squat hold都OK, 咁就可以轉leg press, 慢上慢落, 1:1咁做<br />\n另外多d拉下大腿前後d muscle"},{"pid":"1889cbed3a2ccb562a687e367d2627066434ee82","tid":257993,"uid":50088,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-26T07:35:45.000Z","msg":"睇物理治療啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n其實上面巴打答緊你既野都係物理治療黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"282648044baf95bd7f1d08e1b47c94670db69381","tid":257993,"uid":78574,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-26T07:40:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>一個點痛<br />\n定係成個關節都痛？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n一個點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n岩岩菠蘿蓋對下個個位？<br />\n係咪loading越大越痛，e.g. 跳高落地個陣</blockquote><br />\n我係,想知係咩事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n應該係patellar tendinopathy, <br />\n又或者叫jumpers knee<br />\n即係條patellar tendon 發炎<br />\n依家唔做運動個陣有冇痛？</blockquote><br />\n唔會 大力少少摸就痛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"http://bjsm.bmj.com/content/bjsports/39/2/102/F2.large.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbjsm.bmj.com%2Fcontent%2Fbjsports%2F39%2F2%2F102%2FF2.large.jpg&h=fe9710e1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n再問多少少, <br />\n如果你做A呢個動作, 可以引發到同樣位置既痛<br />\n咁就應該係patellar tendinopathy</blockquote><br />\n我做A會痛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 謝解答<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咁你9成9係patellar tendinopathy<br />\n依家應該要做既係休息+練返條tendon既strength<br />\ne.g. 靠牆坐/squat, 但唔使上落, 淨係hold個動作<br />\n同埋每次做運動都一定要做warm-up, cool down<br />\n帶返走d metabolic waste, 對healing有幫助<br />\n<br />\n如果真係要繼續打波, 可以戴條jumper's knee strap<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.halfpriceperfumes.co.uk/img/p/1/4/4/6/5/0/144650-large.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.halfpriceperfumes.co.uk%2Fimg%2Fp%2F1%2F4%2F4%2F6%2F5%2F0%2F144650-large.jpg&h=a069f43f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n將條strap硬既地方壓係你痛既位正上方<br />\n咁就可以spread開d stress</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 真係好感謝你<br />\n呢個痛都困擾左我兩三年<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n兩三年你都唔搵醫生睇下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nBTW, 坐牆個動作可以做30s- 1min/set, 3 set, rest 1 min<br />\n覺得有進步可以做squat (都係hold), 再來就做單腳squat hold<br />\n如果一轉動作, 24hr後仍然覺得會痛, 咁就做返上一個<br />\n如單腳squat hold都OK, 咁就可以轉leg press, 慢上慢落, 1:1咁做<br />\n另外多d拉下大腿前後d muscle</blockquote><br />\n次次都係打波痛,打完休息下又無事,行得走得<br />\n其實都知應該有D事,但又唔知搵邊個睇好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e1f174c86bc4eccce38590cdbd8202b8f251393a","tid":257993,"uid":82919,"like":0,"dis